snippet: Cara Lewis, who left William Morris Endeavor last month, will be working for its archrival.
abstract: Cara Lewis, who left William Morris Endeavor last month, will be working for its archrival.
lead_paragraph: 1:31 p.m. | Updated Cara Lewis, a top booking agent for hip-hop who last month left her longtime job at WME, the agency formerly known as William Morris Endeavor, has joined that company's archrival, the Creative Artists Agency.
